# Goal Description

Build the **Farm to Table** hyperlocal farmer marketplace full-stack web application. The platform connects consumers with farmers within a 5-7 km radius for direct purchasing of fresh produce.

This implementation will use **PostgreSQL (Supabase)** with **PostGIS** for geospatial queries, and follow a strict, production-ready architecture. The backend will use Express.js with a layered MVC+Services approach. The frontend will use React Vite, Redux Toolkit, React Router, React Hook Form, and Zod, with a **Feature-Based Folder Structure** and **Vertical Sidebar Navigation**.

## User Review Required

- **Scope:** The requested feature set is massive (Wallets, Delivery Zones, Subscriptions, Audit Logs). This plan outlines the structure to support all of them, but implementation will need to be strictly sequenced to ensure quality.

## Proposed Changes

---

### Database Implementation
A comprehensive relational schema using Supabase PostgreSQL.

#### [NEW] [backend/database/schema.sql](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/backend/database/schema.sql)
- Tables: `users`, `farmers`, `consumers`, `products`, `orders`, `order_items`, `payments`, `reviews`, `subscriptions`, `notifications`, `delivery_zones`, `wallet_transactions`, `audit_logs`, `cart_items`.
- PostGIS distance querying (`ST_DWithin`).
- Enums for order states, subscription intervals, and user roles.

---

### Backend Infrastructure
Strict MVC + Services architecture with robust logging and validation.

#### [NEW] `backend/server.js` & [backend/src/app.js](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/backend/src/app.js)
- Express setup, middleware injection, centralized error handling, and server initialization.

#### [NEW] `backend/src/config/`
- [db.js](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/backend/src/config/db.js): PostgreSQL connection pool.
- [logger.js](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/backend/src/config/logger.js): Winston logging configuration.

#### [NEW] `backend/src/middlewares/`
- [authMiddleware.js](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/backend/src/middleware/authMiddleware.js): JWT and role validation.
- [errorMiddleware.js](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/backend/src/middleware/errorMiddleware.js): Global error handler.
- `validationMiddleware.js`: Zod schema validation interceptors.

#### [NEW] `backend/src/utils/`
