#### [NEW] `backend/src/jobs/`
- [subscriptionCron.js](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/backend/src/jobs/subscriptionCron.js): node-cron for automated recurring orders.

---

### Backend APIs (Modular)
Separated controllers, services, repositories, routes, and validators for each domain. Domains will include:
- **Auth**: Registration, login, profile management.
- **Products**: CRUD, location-based nearby search.
- **Orders**: Creation with transactions (locking for stock updates), lifecycle management.
- **Farmers**: Profile management, stats dashboard, delivery zones.
- **Consumers**: Cart management, wallet transactions, subscriptions.
- **Admin**: Approvals, system-wide analytics, audit logs, minimum price enforcement.
- **Notifications**: Email trigger endpoints.
- **Reviews**: Product and farmer feedback.

---

### Frontend Infrastructure (Feature-Based)
React Vite with plain CSS (no Tailwind), organized by feature slices.

#### [NEW] `frontend/src/app/`
- [store.js](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/frontend/src/redux/store.js): Redux Toolkit global store configuration.

#### [NEW] `frontend/src/layouts/`
- `AdminLayout`, `FarmerLayout`, `ConsumerLayout` and `MainLayout`.
- All layouts will implement the **Vertical Sidebar Navigation** component, responsive for mobile (hamburger menu).

#### [NEW] `frontend/src/components/`
- Reusable UI elements: `Sidebar.jsx`, [Button.jsx](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/frontend/src/components/reusable/Button.jsx), [Input.jsx](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/frontend/src/components/reusable/Input.jsx), [ProductCard.jsx](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/frontend/src/components/reusable/ProductCard.jsx), [Modal.jsx](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/frontend/src/components/reusable/Modal.jsx), [Loader.jsx](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/frontend/src/components/reusable/Loader.jsx).

#### [NEW] `frontend/src/features/`
- Each feature directory will contain its respective JSX pages, localized CSS files, and Redux slices where necessary.
- Example structure: `features/auth/`, `features/farmer/`, `features/products/`, etc.

