## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run lint` and `npm run build` on the frontend before finalizing.

### Manual Verification
- Execute [schema.sql](file:///c:/Users/karth/Downloads/6th%20Sem/Full%20stack/farm%20to%20home/backend/database/schema.sql) in Supabase SQL Editor.
- Start backend and verify all API endpoints using Postman or Swagger (if added).
- Start frontend and verify:
  - Landing page visual design.
  - Vertical sidebar navigation responsiveness.
  - Role-based redirection upon login.
  - End-to-end checkout flow using geolocation.


### Frontend UI Phase

- Build ecommerce homepage
- Implement vertical sidebar navigation
- Implement responsive layouts
- Ensure strict mobile compatibility
